parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wipers can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during inclement weather conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat attachment can cause the seat to move unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headrest can cause head injuries or whiplash in the event of an accident or sudden stop.
